# Minimal puckering CV validation: Single mannose ring
# Validates PUCKERING action computes correct Cremer-Pople coordinates
# for comparison against Grothaus et al. 2022 theta distributions
#
# Ring atoms: O5, C1, C2, C3, C4, C5 (standard pyranose order)
# Expected: theta ≈ 0 (4C1 chair dominates at 300K)

puck: PUCKERING ATOMS=1,2,3,4,5,6

PRINT ARG=puck.phi,puck.theta,puck.amplitude STRIDE=100 FILE=COLVAR_pucker FMT=%8.4f
